	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite: Proficiency in @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-rules.JournalEntry.rv19GFzEa0nMTuAF.JournalEntryPage.A5vSPTTu7J1k8HA9#medicine]{Medicine}</strong></em></p><p><em>You spend time during your rest tending to the wounds of your allies.</em></p><p><strong>During a Short Rest</strong> - 1 Creature</p><p>When you and your allies take a short rest, choose one creature who expended at least one hit die to heal, including yourself.</p><ul><li><p>You roll a &amp;reference[medicine] check.</p></li><li><p>The chosen creature regains additional hit points equal to your medicine check total.</p></li></ul>",
